{"tid":2399469,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬化騰給騰訊員工每人發100股，價值7.39萬港元","createTime":"2021-02-08T07:12:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T08:24:13.000Z","uid":91914,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c9a2ea3cb5ae200da9e21b9cbd63cfd39388ec65","tid":2399469,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T07:12:04.000Z","msg":"好公司可以點入 請唔請我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n騰訊員工今日收到陽光普照獎&mdash;&mdash;每位騰訊員工都將得到100股騰訊股票，解禁期一年。據說，這還屬於額外贈與，不屬於年終獎。<br />\n<br />\n針對網上流傳的&ldquo;全員發獎&rdquo;，午後，騰訊回應年終獎發價值超6萬元股票：不是每個人都有。騰訊方面表示，不是每個人都有，公司在今年年終獎中，對做出特別貢獻的員工授予了一筆同心同行獎（100股的一次性激勵）。<br />\n<br />\n當前，騰訊股價約739港元，以此計算，每位騰訊員工獲得了價值7.39萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊曾多次授予員工股票。2017年7月，騰訊發行合計約1787萬股新股，獎勵10800名員工；2016年末，騰訊向每位員工授予每人300股騰訊股票，作為公司成立18周年的特別紀念。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊成立20周年的時候，騰訊也曾給每位員工發放100股。"},{"pid":"685684d533e0872eb661ae9b5a14c14fe2c000e5","tid":2399469,"uid":362827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T07:13:18.000Z","msg":"入去掃地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ce9335f7c0fbd1bbe1efd8b512cd196df65f2c","tid":2399469,"uid":107681,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T07:13:25.000Z","msg":"馬：反正遲早都是黨的，鍾意咪拎囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbdc803842af14a7b67fe62f3c58efd034774399","tid":2399469,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T07:22:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8f89ad437d5f28ee23b63eb20c5b1e91780aac","tid":2399469,"uid":92125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T07:24:43.000Z","msg":"平時都分唔少錢 其實你入FAAMG都係成日派股"},{"pid":"00e0af37a56f13482673f9d866ee37890304d48f","tid":2399469,"uid":72085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":